{"tid":1140960,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"POKÉMON 神探Pikachu","createTime":"2019-05-06T07:16:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T16:00:43.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9a74efd4ff04431154f8bca75e0a283291acc9c8","tid":1140960,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T07:16:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://movie.yahoo-leisure.hk/assets/poster/MV5BMTk1MjgwNjM2MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzMyODM3NjM@._V1_SY1000_CR0,0,674,1000_AL_5770480916933837013_380x560.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmovie.yahoo-leisure.hk%2Fassets%2Fposter%2FMV5BMTk1MjgwNjM2MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzMyODM3NjM%40._V1_SY1000_CR0%2C0%2C674%2C1000_AL_5770480916933837013_380x560.jpg&h=219c7047&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n導演 :<br />\n    羅伯萊特曼<br />\n演員 :<br />\n    賴恩尼諾斯, 積提斯史密夫, 嘉芙蓮紐頓, 雪琪禾達侯絲, 奧馬查柏羅, 基斯吉爾, 渡邊謙, 標尼菲<br />\n片長 :<br />\n    --<br />\n級別 :<br />\n    --<br />\n語言 :<br />\n    粵語<br />\n上映 :<br />\n    9.5.2019 (公映) <br />\n<br />\n故事簡介<br />\n<br />\n神探Harry Goodman神秘失蹤，他21歲的兒子Tim決心查出真相。他得到爸爸的精靈助手 &ndash; 幽默活潑、可愛又迷糊的神探 Pikachu協助調查。只有Tim才能聽到Pikachu說話，於是他們聯手一起去破解這個複雜的謎團。他們於人類和POK&Eacute;MON和諧共存的瑞美市追查線索，遇到各種各樣的POK&Eacute;MON，揭發了一個足以破壞人類和POK&Eacute;MON和諧共存，威脅整個POK&Eacute;MON宇宙的驚天陰謀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SZVHkVj3_FA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSZVHkVj3_FA&d=JxdAuiyzJYRXF2tJvMOkN34HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=468711bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SZVHkVj3_FA</a>"},{"pid":"3bd4d6f4594e251c5018b784131bf0e81d71073d","tid":1140960,"uid":52122,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T07:17:54.000Z","msg":"老老實實 呢套野對我黎講幾吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係噴火龍啲皮膚做得有啲柒之外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f55ee52307fc23c8df9ba9f47b9c41fc13d10c7d","tid":1140960,"uid":34243